ygData.messageBody:
Hello to all<br> <br> I have a Druid that is lvl
18 and would like ideas of places to visit to get
more exp and money since ive heard that my next spells
r going to be expensive and from lvl 24 and up will
become more expensive. Im currently in Oasis and
sometimes visit Najena with my guild, I heard that Lake
Rathe is a very cool place to be and Cazic Thule but Im
not so sure about the later. <br>Well thanks in
advance for any info u may give me and may Tunare protect
you all.<br><br>Kyrianie, Druid of the Fourth Circle
